title: 223.4 VOX Mini: "Biblical" Womanhood
description:
Happy New Year to YOU! We thought we'd start of 2020 with a soft, non-controversial topic in which we have very apathetic opinions of: What it means to be a "Biblical" Woman.

So much in those quotations, right? ;)

You can watch us hash this out here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hTmLQcaTt-k&feature=youtu.be
